    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 that features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and screams to an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. To ensure mechanical longevity, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced. The chassis remains remarkably composed, utilizing a variable M differential lock and refreshed multi-link rear suspension bushings for precise turn-in and corner-exit stability. While showing minor cosmetic evidence of spirited road use, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the driver who prioritizes mechanical excellence and analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
