    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, with just the usual minor wear you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable, stylish ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
