    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8. This naturally aspirated powerhouse utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut with responsive damping, and the 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement through a short-throw shifter. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction and torque vectoring during high-lateral-G cornering. Recent service includes preventative maintenance on the rod bearings and a comprehensive fluid flush of the cooling and hydraulic systems. The suspension geometry is maintained to factory specifications, offering communicative steering feedback and excellent turn-in response. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain and structural integrity are robust, making this a driver-focused example optimized for both the circuit and spirited canyon runs.",
